    <TextView
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="SIG SELECTION"
        android:textStyle="bold"
        android:textColor="@color/black"
        android:textSize="50dp"
        android:paddingLeft="20dp"
        android:paddingTop="20dp"
        ></TextView>

    <TextView
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="*NOTE:- SIG TECH is mandatory for all you can choose 2 more SIG'S other that SIG TECH
. SIG GRAPH AND SIG WEB ARE bind together ,So if you choose SIG WEB than SIG GRAPH is compulsory and viceversa
 You can have maximum of 3 SIG'S and minimum of 1 that is SIG TECH."
